!
service password-encryption
!
no ip domain lookup
ip domain name cml.lab
!
ip ssh version 2
!
logging console
!
username cisco privilege 15 password cisco
!
line con 0
 exec-timeout 0 0
 logging synchronous

line vty 0 4
 exec-timeout 0 0
 logging synchronous
 login local
 transport input ssh
!
logging 10.0.0.149
!
alias exec q exit
!
crypto key generate rsa modulus 2048 exportable
!
end
